---
layout: layouts/component-demo.njk
title: Vital Sign — Systolic BP View
description: number display of systolic blood pressure in millimetres of mercury (mmHg)
---

{% from "components/vital-sign-blood-pressure-systolic-as-mmhg-view/macro.njk" import vitalSignBloodPressureSystolicAsMmhgView %}

<h2>Normal</h2>
<p>{{ vitalSignBloodPressureSystolicAsMmhgView({
  value: 118,
  label: "Systolic BP"
}) }}</p>

<h2>Elevated</h2>
<p>{{ vitalSignBloodPressureSystolicAsMmhgView({
  value: 145,
  label: "Systolic BP (elevated)",
  classes: "elevated"
}) }}</p>

<h2>Accessibility</h2>
<p>The unit is wrapped in
  <code>&lt;abbr title="millimetres of mercury"&gt;mmHg&lt;/abbr&gt;</code>
  so screen readers expand the abbreviation correctly.</p>
